  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351170/extras/d415c9b7366debb6059e14acafc57259.poster.avif?t=1710051108\" width=594 height=132 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351170/extras/d415c9b7366debb6059e14acafc57259.webm?t=1710051108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351170/extras/d415c9b7366debb6059e14acafc57259.mp4?t=1710051108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Choose your jet, suit up & get into the thick of it. Doomsday Jetlag follows lone heroes as they dogfight the hounds of hell coming to bring nuclear armageddon to the lands below. Along the way, skill up your pilot to attain radical upgrades to make the fight a little more even, bolster the defenses of the lands you are protecting & find cards to equip powerful abilities in your next runs!<br><br>After a hard day's work saving the good people back on terra firma take your winnings back to the hangar and buy new jets or upgrade old ones for your next round of heroism. Fight off all kinds of jets, bombers, ships, missiles & nuclear warheads in your quest to delay the end of the world from your cockpit, one burst of molten lead at a time!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351170/extras/7fea7a94e701a6eee592821f32d7007a.poster.avif?t=1710051108\" width=594 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351170/extras/7fea7a94e701a6eee592821f32d7007a.webm?t=1710051108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351170/extras/7fea7a94e701a6eee592821f32d7007a.mp4?t=1710051108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Collect useful abilities and power-ups to aid you in battle!<br>Mix & Match each round with 5 ability slots to create powerful combos and deal deadly damage.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351170/extras/4639b10dacd9a516725ef4f861a7da72.poster.avif?t=1710051108\" width=594 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351170/extras/4639b10dacd9a516725ef4f861a7da72.webm?t=1710051108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351170/extras/4639b10dacd9a516725ef4f861a7da72.mp4?t=1710051108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Save the world and use your reward money to upgrade your jets or buy new ones!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351170/extras/576e928c1a49b7f77c2d547ac2bf21ea.poster.avif?t=1710051108\" width=594 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351170/extras/576e928c1a49b7f77c2d547ac2bf21ea.webm?t=1710051108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351170/extras/576e928c1a49b7f77c2d547ac2bf21ea.mp4?t=1710051108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>As you level up your jets attempt missions across the world in more challenging maps!<br>Play across 11 Classic mode maps & 6 Onslaught mode maps defending a total of 166 Cities & Regions all across the world!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351170/extras/a60d065808581c8ebf3c340f6f126427.poster.avif?t=1710051108\" width=594 height=132 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351170/extras/a60d065808581c8ebf3c340f6f126427.webm?t=1710051108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351170/extras/a60d065808581c8ebf3c340f6f126427.mp4?t=1710051108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351170/extras/d415c9b7366debb6059e14acafc57259.poster.avif?t=1710051108\" width=594 height=132 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351170/extras/d415c9b7366debb6059e14acafc57259.webm?t=1710051108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351170/extras/d415c9b7366debb6059e14acafc57259.mp4?t=1710051108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Choose your jet, suit up & get into the thick of it. Doomsday Jetlag follows lone heroes as they dogfight the hounds of hell coming to bring nuclear armageddon to the lands below. Along the way, skill up your pilot to attain radical upgrades to make the fight a little more even, bolster the defenses of the lands you are protecting & find cards to equip powerful abilities in your next runs!<br><br>After a hard day's work saving the good people back on terra firma take your winnings back to the hangar and buy new jets or upgrade old ones for your next round of heroism. Fight off all kinds of jets, bombers, ships, missiles & nuclear warheads in your quest to delay the end of the world from your cockpit, one burst of molten lead at a time!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351170/extras/7fea7a94e701a6eee592821f32d7007a.poster.avif?t=1710051108\" width=594 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351170/extras/7fea7a94e701a6eee592821f32d7007a.webm?t=1710051108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351170/extras/7fea7a94e701a6eee592821f32d7007a.mp4?t=1710051108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Collect useful abilities and power-ups to aid you in battle!<br>Mix & Match each round with 5 ability slots to create powerful combos and deal deadly damage.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351170/extras/4639b10dacd9a516725ef4f861a7da72.poster.avif?t=1710051108\" width=594 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351170/extras/4639b10dacd9a516725ef4f861a7da72.webm?t=1710051108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351170/extras/4639b10dacd9a516725ef4f861a7da72.mp4?t=1710051108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Save the world and use your reward money to upgrade your jets or buy new ones!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351170/extras/576e928c1a49b7f77c2d547ac2bf21ea.poster.avif?t=1710051108\" width=594 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351170/extras/576e928c1a49b7f77c2d547ac2bf21ea.webm?t=1710051108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351170/extras/576e928c1a49b7f77c2d547ac2bf21ea.mp4?t=1710051108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>As you level up your jets attempt missions across the world in more challenging maps!<br>Play across 11 Classic mode maps & 6 Onslaught mode maps defending a total of 166 Cities & Regions all across the world!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351170/extras/a60d065808581c8ebf3c340f6f126427.poster.avif?t=1710051108\" width=594 height